00:40:06,960 --> 00:40:08,880
Isn't that Ton who got banned?

541
00:40:09,809 --> 00:40:12,119
I didn't expect to see him back on
the court.

542
00:40:14,079 --> 00:40:15,159
Palamit.

543
00:40:16,329 --> 00:40:18,440
They're good at shooting
under the hoop.

544
00:40:18,960 --> 00:40:20,519
Just follow the game plan, okay?

545
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:22,039
- Yes, Coach!
- Yes, Coach!

546
00:40:41,119 --> 00:40:43,769
Today's game is
between Palamit School,

547
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:45,039
known for their excellence
at shooting under the hoop,

548
00:40:45,159 --> 00:40:48,329
and the other school, Tanwarin
Wittaya, is the underdog.

549
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:54,159
Stay tuned, and that includes
everyone watching remotely.

550
00:40:54,440 --> 00:40:55,840
Let's see how things turn out.

551
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:57,079
Are you okay?

552
00:40:59,239 --> 00:41:00,599
I'm a bit scared.

553
00:41:01,199 --> 00:41:02,559
I don't know if we can beat them.

554
00:41:04,679 --> 00:41:07,199
Don't be scared. We can do this.

555
00:41:08,769 --> 00:41:09,880
Come on. Let's get warmed up.

556
00:41:32,840 --> 00:41:33,840
Ryu!

557
00:41:37,239 --> 00:41:38,239
Zen!

558
00:41:39,329 --> 00:41:40,440
Shoot!

559
00:41:41,289 --> 00:41:43,079
- Zen!
- Zen, over here!

560
00:41:44,639 --> 00:41:45,639
Zen!

561
00:41:46,809 --> 00:41:47,809
Zen!

562
00:41:50,289 --> 00:41:51,599
- Zen!
- Hey!

563
00:41:54,960 --> 00:41:56,289
Why didn't he pass the ball?

564
00:41:57,000 --> 00:41:58,199
He kept staring.

565
00:42:00,519 --> 00:42:02,440
Calm down, Zen! Hang in there!

566
00:42:08,239 --> 00:42:12,639
Wow! Palamit did it again!

567
00:42:12,719 --> 00:42:15,840
They're looking great today.

568
00:42:23,199 --> 00:42:24,199
Go.

569
00:42:27,559 --> 00:42:29,329
So, what's next?

570
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:35,400
- Whoa.
- Hey!

571
00:42:40,679 --> 00:42:42,039
It's okay!

572
00:42:42,119 --> 00:42:45,400
As you can see,
for Tanwarin Wittaya,

573
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:48,289
their players are mostly new.

574
00:42:48,440 --> 00:42:50,679
Why the change? Do you know?

575
00:42:50,809 --> 00:42:54,079
The old team was caught
using narcotics.

576
00:42:54,119 --> 00:42:56,480
- Oh.
- So they were expelled.

577
00:42:56,519 --> 00:42:58,039
And a new team was formed.

578
00:42:58,119 --> 00:43:00,329
That's why there are many new
players on the team.

579
00:43:00,599 --> 00:43:02,920
- Jedi. Status report.
- Yes, Coach?

580
00:43:04,360 --> 00:43:05,960
Our team committed a lot of fouls.

581
00:43:06,329 --> 00:43:08,960
Traveling and reaching in.

582
00:43:09,559 --> 00:43:11,039
They're losing their shot.

583
00:43:12,239 --> 00:43:13,920
What's wrong with Zen today?

584
00:43:22,639 --> 00:43:26,039
Hey, what's up with Zen today?
He keeps messing up.

585
00:43:26,119 --> 00:43:27,719
Right? Are they going to be okay?

586
00:43:36,559 --> 00:43:37,559
Zen!

587
00:43:38,599 --> 00:43:39,599
Hang in there!

588
00:43:40,119 --> 00:43:41,960
Aw!

589
00:43:42,039 --> 00:43:43,558
He must be Zen's boyfriend!

590
00:43:43,559 --> 00:43:44,559
Definitely.

591
00:43:46,719 --> 00:43:47,719
Time's up.

592
00:44:00,679 --> 00:44:01,679
Zen,

593
00:44:02,360 --> 00:44:03,800
what's up with you?

594
00:44:04,039 --> 00:44:05,559
Why are you playing like that?

595
00:44:06,760 --> 00:44:08,000
I'm sorry, Coach.

596
00:44:10,800 --> 00:44:13,800
I know how important
this game is to you,

597
00:44:14,119 --> 00:44:17,320
to our team, and to our club.

598
00:44:18,199 --> 00:44:19,519
But let me tell you.

599
00:44:19,880 --> 00:44:21,719
If that's how you're going to play,

600
00:44:22,599 --> 00:44:25,079
then this might be your last game.

601
00:44:25,519 --> 00:44:26,960
Do you understand what I said?

602
00:44:27,440 --> 00:44:28,559
- Yes, Coach.
- Yes, Coach.

603
00:44:31,920 --> 00:44:33,159
- Coach.
- Hm?

604
00:44:34,360 --> 00:44:35,639
Can I talk to Zen for a bit?

605
00:44:36,480 --> 00:44:37,480
Zen.

606
00:44:44,239 --> 00:44:46,039
Ow. Hey!

607
00:44:46,880 --> 00:44:47,960
Ryu!

608
00:44:52,559 --> 00:44:54,199
Just tell me off already!

609
00:45:06,800 --> 00:45:08,199
Didn't you tell me

610
00:45:08,880 --> 00:45:10,719
your dad would hold you like this

611
00:45:11,079 --> 00:45:12,760
when you were upset?

612
00:45:18,119 --> 00:45:19,159
Ryu...

613
00:45:20,360 --> 00:45:21,480
Hold me tight.

614
00:45:29,519 --> 00:45:31,280
I'm scared we're going to lose.

615
00:45:31,360 --> 00:45:32,400
Shh!

616
00:45:32,880 --> 00:45:34,039
Don't be.

617
00:45:35,920 --> 00:45:37,719
We'll do our best.

618
00:46:21,519 --> 00:46:24,159
Ryu, you're not going to bail on me

619
00:46:24,199 --> 00:46:25,599
like you did in middle school if we
make it to finals again, are you?

620
00:46:25,920 --> 00:46:27,079
I promise.

621
00:46:28,559 --> 00:46:31,760
Both Coach Ton and the club
are going to go.

622
00:46:31,880 --> 00:46:33,920
The school board has issued an order

623
00:46:34,119 --> 00:46:36,519
for Coach Ton to be relieved of his
duties immediately.

624
00:46:36,639 --> 00:46:37,880
Aren't you going
to help at all, sir?

625
00:46:38,039 --> 00:46:39,840
The decision isn't even final.

626
00:46:39,920 --> 00:46:40,920
Can you help Coach, Mom?

627
00:46:40,960 --> 00:46:43,239
If I help, what are you going to
give me in exchange?

628
00:46:43,320 --> 00:46:47,360
Now that you're all here, I'd like
to begin Coach Ton's investigation.
